183 13. The collaborating physician shall determine and document the completion of a
184 period of time during which the physician assistant shall practice with the collaborating
185 physician continuously present before practicing in a setting where the collaborating
186 physician is not continuously present. This limitation shall not apply to collaborative
187 arrangements of providers of population-based public health services as defined by 20 CSR
